beer.beer_description: Pomelo is a brand new Grapefruit and Lime Gose, brewed for ultimate summer sour refreshment. We've taken the base recipe from our house favourite, Seaside, and swapped in some beautiful pink grapefruit. This little baby is made for summer sipping. It has an incredible balance between tart acidity and citrus blast with the perfect mix of grapefruit and lime. The back end is as thirst quenching as anything you'll find on a hot day and we can see many cans of this being consumed in or next to a body of water!
